pddl.prompt:
You are the orchestrator. Here are the public environment facts:
{environment->public_information}
Here are the move proposals from the agents (exact text they produced):
{plan_agent_1}
{plan_agent_2}
{plan_agent_3}
Your goal:
{agents->orchestrator->goal}
Integrate the agents' proposed moves and produce a correct PDDL domain and PDDL problem targeting the FastDownwards solver. Keep actions made by different agents distinct in the domain and ensure preconditions enforce: only top disk may be moved, cannot place larger disk on smaller disk, and only the agent allowed to move a specific disk may execute actions that move that disk. Enclose the PDDL domain between <domain></domain> tags, and the PDDL problem between <problem></problem> tags.
